"#####Keybinds#####
"change insert mode to normal mode with Ctrl+j
inoremap <C-j> <ESC>
"move cursor on logical line basis
nnoremap j gj
nnoremap k gk
nnoremap gj j
nnoremap gk k
"centering next search result by n, N
nnoremap n nzz
nnoremap N Nzz
"cut and yank a word
nnoremap xx vawx 
nnoremap yy vawy
"move to other windows
nnoremap , <C-w>h
nnoremap . <C-w>l

